    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. Validation evidence demonstrates Pearson r = 0.97 and R² = 0.94 for normalised hemolysis index across five operating points, with RMSE of 3.2% of mean measured NHI. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device and that the simulation results support the tolerance decision under the RH < 1 acceptance criterion.",
